args:
No matter how many fiends we waylay,
they will continue coming unless we can
destroy the otherworldly boxes that are
causing the mana to warp.
Okay then. You take care of the boxes,\nand I'll make sure you stay alive!
My fate is in your hands.
There. The job is finished without mishap.
The way you moved just now.\nMight you be...?
Ohmigosh, did you FINALLY notice?\nSo yeah, I guess my ancestors used\nto serve you or whatever.
How long has this truth been\nrevealed to you?

Well, my original reason for traveling
around was 'cause I was supposed to
＂find the queen.＂ So naturally I had a
description of said queen.
Yeaaah, so here's the thing: I wasn't\nsuper into hunting down old royalty\nuntil I met you.

I mostly just claimed to be looking for
you while I was sightseeing. That's why
I kept taking all those pictures—so I had
proof I was at least doing SOMETHING.
But then I totally DID find you!\nSuper lucky, right?
Why did you not share this\nwith me from the beginning?
Because once I found you...\nmy trip would be over.
If you are ＂sort of＂ joking, may I also\nassume you are ＂sort of＂ speaking sooth?
Look, I didn't get into all this because\nI knew your memories were fuzzy.

I decided to just kinda...I dunno.
Watch and wait, I guess. I needed
to see if you even still WANTED to
be a queen after all this time.
If you preferred to leave all that behind,\nI was totally happy to let you do it.
...It is not that I wish to forget my past.
Yeah. I understand what you told me.
So...I wanna let you know something.
You think your memories are just\na burden to you, right?
And that whenever you look back,\nall you find is sadness and stuff.
But I know that's not true.\nIt can't be.
I mean, yeah, I know you feel sad when\nyou look back 'cause you think about all\nthe people you didn't want to lose.
Look, I get it: You loved all these\npeople once, and now they're gone—\nand that is TOTALLY depressing.
But you shouldn't walk around like\nyou didn't have any GOOD memories.

Anyway, that's why we should take a pic!
You'll never be sad or lonely with me,
and if we do this together, I know you'll
still be able to look toward the future.

Because once you take one picture,
you'll wanna take more—and before
you know it, you end up with a whole
boatload of awesome memories!

You truly are unshakable! No matter
how sage your words, you always
manage to direct the conversation
back to taking a picture.
Because it always comes back to that!\nEven for a lonely old lady like you.
Heh. I suppose I may have earned that,\nyou insolent maid.
Very well. I shall recognize your case\nand allow us a picture together.
Yessss! Let's consider it a commemorative\nphoto, of the day you finally lifted the ban\non having your likeness taken!
Do not hope overmuch, Nadine;\nit is but a single picture.
Aw, c'mon! No one stops at one!\nLemme have ten. ...Or a hundred.
I have one thing to say ere you begin...
You must ensure that I look cute.
Cute? Girl, you're gonna be GORGE!
Marry, but you are standing\never so close to me...
Besties gotta stand close! ...Oh, wait!\nHere, take your hand and use it to make\na heart with mine like... Yeah, there!
Pray do not tarry, lest I change my mind...
